org.openstreetmap.osm.data.coordinates
Class Bounds

java.lang.Object
  org.openstreetmap.osm.data.coordinates.Bounds
Direct Known Subclasses:
PolygonBounds
public class Bounds
extends java.lang.Object

This is a simple data class for "rectangular" areas of the world, given in lat/lon min/max values. Do not confuse this with "Area", which is an OSM-primitive for a vector of nodes, describing some area (like a sea).

Author:
imi
